Class StatsViewController

java.lang.Object
com.rocketshipcheckingtool.ui.roles.technician.StatsViewController
public class StatsViewController extends Object
Controller class for managing the statistics view in the technician role. Handles the initialization and configuration of various charts and the scaling of SVG graphics.
